  "instructions": [
    "Heat 1 tablespoon of olive oil in a large hot pot vessel over medium heat.",
    "Add the garlic and cook for 1 minute until fragrant.",
    "Add the Mediterranean-spiced sausage and cook until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the rice and cook for 2 minutes, stirring constantly.",
    "Add 2 cups of water and bring to a boil. ",
    "Reduce heat to low, cover, and simmer for 20 minutes.",
    "While the paella is cooking, air-fry the shrimp until pink and cooked through.",
    "Stir in yeast, vinaigrette dressing, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Taste and adjust seasoning as needed.",
    "Serve the paella hot, garnished with chopped fresh parsley and air-fried shrimp on top."
